Debugging via Chrome Dev Tools

timers:  3:15 mins
timer check: 7:54 mins

shortcut commands:

    node inspect                                                only in node.js cmd
    node --inspect-brk (playground/21debugging.js)              with chrome dev tool
    nodemon --inspect-brk (playground/21debugging.js)
    clear 
    nodemon --inspect-brk 21applec21.js read --title="to buy"
    
    ctl + c  ---> ^C                                            (to quit)
    
    for chrome browser
    chrome://inspect/#devices
    click on { play icon }
    in colsole below type: note.body = "Something else"
    
    click on --> open dedicated devTools for Node
    not ---> inspect

